Problem Solving
Analytical Skills
Ethical Conduct
Communication Proficiency
Technical Capacity
Collaboration
Time Management
Leadership
Business Acumen
Decision Making
Required Education and Experience
Bachelor's Degree in Mechanical or Chemical Engineering.
Master’s degree in Chemical Engineering a plus
Minimum of 4-5 years work experience.
Must have excellent written and verbal communication skills
